entries.title_d: Storm Squadron has been charged with security of the Endor system and the Empire's new top secret project. You are to fly patrol duty in the Endor system and keep a close watch out for any suspicious activity.
entries.title: Endor System: Patrol the Endor System
entries.split_quest_alert: Alert! Enemy fighters detected. Incoming at attack speed.
entries.quest_patrol_d: When you reach a navigation waypoint you will receive a new one to the next location. Follow the patrol waypoints until you come to the end of your patrol.
entries.quest_location_d: Travel to the Endor system and follow the patrol navigation waypoints. As you reach one navigation waypoint, you will get a new waypoint to the next location on the patrol route.
